{"tid":2208850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人認為自己雖身在人世但好透明 已死","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:10:36.000Z","uid":365546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4573fbf67cb43d02c59cec24d6462f38504f270","tid":2208850,"uid":365546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"世界上有些人好像明星一樣，我們能清楚說比如曾經在IFC見過鍾楚紅一次。<br />\n<br />\n而我跟某人已經見過63次，我很清楚知道次數，然而對方還是不知道我是誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n有一次在某店見到某人，我舉起手打招呼，對方望望後面以為我跟其他人say hi, 再直行直往買雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我再次鼓起勇氣等到某人出黎，再say hi. 怎知道對方雙眼只盯着杯外賣雪糕唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n點解連杯雪糕都比我重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要某m店雪糕全部消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如何看上去能令人一眼便知道我是誰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d5be918b745f1f12ce9ecd71bc9984ecccb69","tid":2208850,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"對方男定女呀？"},{"pid":"0db1ff39b5556450bde6ead96b88f9e6e1070c78","tid":2208850,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"潮文？"},{"pid":"0c0a5e7acd6d35a0493ea244d93e2622ac2cf518","tid":2208850,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"琴日有個同事走咗，佢做咗10年<br />\n但會上都只係噏左幾句客套說話，安排點樣跟進工作，跟住大家如常做嘢，只係冇乜野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺非常唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49399af245e3628c9712451abf2448edd6d436ce","tid":2208850,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"死前要拉走幾個狗官"},{"pid":"5172a5df34b0c9710824b56d48c770d7467687f2","tid":2208850,"uid":321161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"如果冇左女朋友 我都覺得自己唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb42677dc9d1759dbb969ac3a0ad0fc25f1e2b5","tid":2208850,"uid":365546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c0a5e7acd6d35a0493ea244d93e2622ac2cf518","tid":2208850,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"琴日有個同事走咗，佢做咗10年<br />\n但會上都只係噏左幾句客套說話，安排點樣跟進工作，跟住大家如常做嘢，只係冇乜野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺非常唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"有d人在世或離世都彷如無聲。<br />\n<br />\n我為佢做咁多野，佢依然當我透明。<br />\n<br />\n人生真係好唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n我好想喊。<br />\n<br />\n我求神讓佢注意下我。"},{"pid":"957fcbbdcfaa6d358d232bfdcb076b7d8cc603f5","tid":2208850,"uid":365546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5d5be918b745f1f12ce9ecd71bc9984ecccb69","tid":2208850,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"對方男定女呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"女<br />\n<br />\n女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高高在上的女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}